Getting Started

This section helps you get started with the ultra package.

Example Code 

library(ultra)
data("results")
ULTRAplot(results)

Citing ultra

This package was developed through research performed in the Center for Experimental and Molecular Medicine at the Amsterdam University Medical Center.

If you use this package please cite using:

 citation("ultra")
